    brain: "Brain tasks seem easier today thanks to high estrogen pushing your mental abilities into superhuman territory. Your superb memory, learning ability, mental speed, creativity and eloquence will surprise even you at times. While high estrogen is generally beneficial for your brain skills, there is one way an elevated level of this hormone can have a negative effect: It can make concentration more difficult. For example, you might notice it takes more effort to rein in your thoughts or to focus on a task for an extended period of time. When this happens, just chalk it up to high hormones, then do something to help settle your mind and direct your attention, for example, take a short mental break or promise yourself some kind of reward when you get through the task.",
