    sex: "Cancel some meetings and cross off a few to-dos. You need to make more time in your schedule for sexual fun. That's because throughout your entire Week 2, sensual pleasures — either alone or with a partner — are going to feel more intense and fulfilling than any other days of your cycle. Credit goes to high-and-rising estrogen, which helps send more blood to your nether regions, making them more sensitive.",
