    brain: "If there was ever a time to challenge someone to a brain game or try to outshine someone on a project, it's during your Week 2. Now is when estrogen reaches a level that makes you better at most activities that require stellar mental skills. That's because this hormone fuels several key areas of the brain that improve your memory, learning ability, creativity and verbal skills. If, however, the game or task requires lots of focus on fine or boring details, then you may need to push yourself a little harder to excel since high estrogen can cause mental antsiness, making it difficult to concentrate.",
