    sex: "So many things come so much easier in your Week 2 — your brain skills, your energy, your ability to say tongue-twisters without giving your tongue a cramp. But, you'll probably enjoy the way your high hormones are making it easier to orgasm most of all. And, lucky you, these easier-to-achieve orgasms also happen to produce a bigger, longer-lasting explosion of physical sensations when they occur.",
    career: "Continuing a Week 2 trend, you tend to be happier with your job, school or project today. Or at least more positive about where you're headed and how your current tasks can help you get there. You've got energy to burn — but, it's not going to last much longer! As soon as Week 3 hits, you experience a serious mental and physical slowdown. This makes it a perfect day to finish tasks that require extra high-hormone oomph while you've still got it.",
